le=\"box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;background: none transparent;min-height: unset;object-fit: contain;width: 702.031px;height: auto;\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"750\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9d026c76&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FrwnawOsSCFrBt7hIgyyOl5rlDDp9ZN5qEXtziaY8WFqss2qH8CXZAorC3I6iaO2eibZ835ibkqM1XIATxCAqOwB22g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  </figure>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6k1n88\"><b mpa-font-style=\"minydswhiob\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Siri频频“听不懂人话”的掉线表现，不仅磨光了果粉的情怀，也终于逼得库克彻底“破防”了。</span></span></b></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6k1esy\"><span mpa-font-style=\"minydswhttn\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">本周一，苹果突然宣布重磅人事调整：执掌AI帅印7年的老将约翰·詹南德雷亚（John Giannandrea）正式卸任。</span></span></b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">为了扭转颓势，苹果罕见地从竞争对手阵营挖来了“外援”——</span></span><b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">拥有谷歌DeepMind 和微软双重背景的实战派阿马尔·苏布拉马尼亚（Amar Subramanya），将接棒出任 AI 副总裁。</span></span></b></span></p>\n  <figure style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6k1vie\">\n   <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"503047903\" data-ratio=\"0.44\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;background: none transparent;min-height: unset;object-fit: contain;width: 702.031px;height: auto;\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"750\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9958b009&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FrwnawOsSCFrBt7hIgyyOl5rlDDp9ZN5q3VARic9j8ibDRIcQavLur4uic6ibjzCfMhjJ8HFDVfCzYen2HfILgB1TYA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  </figure>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6kkxg\"><span mpa-font-style=\"minydswh1m1r\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">这一人事变动发生在一个极其敏感的时刻。外界普遍认为苹果在 AI 赛道上已经“掉队”，</span></span><b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">而新上任的苏布拉马尼亚能否在强敌环伺中帮助苹果翻盘，成为了所有人关注的焦点。</span></span></b></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6k1p5\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"502851486\" data-ratio=\"0.15204678362573099\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"684\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=068d1b16&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FrwnawOsSCFp4iatBAbsJzvVraDq6Xh5OHp8QJSvdPzF1icMb5w3x1Umm9iblCmmT5TicezNBeKzhc5teZXS1PElhxw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6k1emg\"><b mpa-font-style=\"minydswh19mt\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-size:20px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"minyoh0pnos\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minyoh0w1z2\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">临危受命的“救火队长”</span></span></b></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6kc08\"><b mpa-font-style=\"minydswh3lh\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">谁是苏布拉马尼亚？</span></span></b></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6k1mu9\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"minydswh1czj\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">他是一位印度裔 AI 研究科学家，以在机器学习、自然语言处理（NLP）和大规模 AI 系统开发领域的成就而著称。</span></span></p>\n  <figure style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6kq63\">\n   <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"503047905\" data-ratio=\"0.5616666666666666\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"600\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: middle; background: none transparent; min-height: unset; object-fit: contain; width: 702.031px; pointer-events: initial;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7ecd3775&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FrwnawOsSCFrBt7hIgyyOl5rlDDp9ZN5qQv7ZMXwYSTxB9EO2KRoibWnyicTJKfgQ97ibj94I8YK2boibb2JlKpGfiag%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  </figure>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6k1svr\"><span mpa-font-style=\"minydswhsk5\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">LinkedIn 资料显示，这位新任苹果 AI 副总裁履历光鲜且硬核。在加入苹果之前，他曾在微软短暂任职，但其职业生涯最浓墨重彩的一笔是在谷歌度过了16年。</span></span><b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">苏布拉马尼亚不仅曾是谷歌 DeepMind 团队的一员，更曾领导过谷歌 Gemini 模型的工程团队。</span></span></b></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6k36p\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"minydswh9gm\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">可以说，这是一位真正懂大模型、懂底层技术的实战派。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6k1i85\"><span mpa-font-style=\"minydswh1vt1\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">值得玩味的是苹果 AI 汇报线的变化。</span></span></b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">&nbsp;前任詹南德雷亚是直接向 CEO 蒂姆·库克（Tim Cook）汇报的高级副总裁；而新任的苏布拉马尼亚将向软件工程主管克雷格·费德里吉（Craig Federighi）汇报。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6k15vy\"><span mpa-font-style=\"minydswh11f9\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">这一架构调整释放了一个明确信号：苹果正在将 AI 从一个独立的战略部门，深度整合进软件产品线。</span></span></b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">&nbsp;库克在声明中也直言，费德里吉在推动 AI 工作中发挥了关键作用，未来将由他统领团队，在明年为用户带来更个性化的 Siri。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6kxn9\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"minydswhq06\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">@CHItraders则在社交媒体X爆料称，苹果此次换帅实际上是在对人工智能团队进行重大重组。公司故作姿态，看似一切如常，实则悄然更换了人工智能团队一半的成员。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6k23rj\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"minydswh1dcc\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">他直言，“苹果这次是直接给AI部门重装系统，根本懒得搞什么“重启”的虚招。”</span></span></p>\n  <figure style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6k10pu\">\n   <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"503047906\" data-ratio=\"1.068\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;background: none transparent;min-height: unset;object-fit: contain;width: 702.031px;height: auto;\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"750\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ff3e5ed3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FrwnawOsSCFrBt7hIgyyOl5rlDDp9ZN5qcm82K5bphwwwibP0BqUKnoQI07hfwE65Xmykic46auetzOMjDeNiar1NQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  </figure>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6kuu8\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"502851485\" data-ratio=\"0.15204678362573099\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"684\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b32c57a5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FrwnawOsSCFp4iatBAbsJzvVraDq6Xh5OHe8dmhZIvx7iacyxC16ia2UjD7RPRrHRnpI5hPAqMqiaNcFDlXwVhCTZvQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6kuc5\"><b mpa-font-style=\"minydswhawj\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-size:20px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"minypfn417xj\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minypfnm1nlj\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">苹果的“焦虑时刻”：</span></span></b></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6kuc5\"><b mpa-font-style=\"minydswhawj\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-size:20px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"minypfn417xj\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minypfnm1nlj\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">不仅是掉队</span></span></b></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6kue0\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"minydswh13nu\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">这次换帅，正值苹果 AI 领域面临巨大的舆论与产品压力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6k1ar\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"minydswhkz4\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">自2022年 OpenAI 发布 ChatGPT 引爆行业以来，微软、谷歌、Meta 等科技巨头纷纷重金押注。相比之下，苹果的反应被业界公认为“迟缓”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6k1m4m\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"minydswh1nal\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">虽然苹果在2024年推出 Apple Intelligence，试图追赶 OpenAI 和谷歌的步伐，但目前的市场反馈并不理想：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6kafn\"><span mpa-font-style=\"minydswhidg\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">·&nbsp;</span></span><b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">用户口碑平平</span></span></b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">现有功能被认为缺乏惊艳感。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6k1zj3\"><span mpa-font-style=\"minydswhlim\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">·&nbsp;</span></span><b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">核心功能跳票</span></span></b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">作为 Apple Intelligence 最关键的一环，升级版 Siri 据称已推迟到2026年才能发布。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6k11tx\"><span mpa-font-style=\"minydswh1xj4\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">这种延迟直接暴露出苹果内部开发 AI 存在的巨大问题。市场研究公司 Seaport Research 分析师简·古德伯格（Jay Goldberg）一针见血地指出：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">“</span></span><b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">问题根源在于，苹果似乎并不知道自己的 AI 战略到底是什么。</span></span></b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">”</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6k75u\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"502851487\" data-ratio=\"0.15204678362573099\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"684\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=79f3dc0f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FrwnawOsSCFp4iatBAbsJzvVraDq6Xh5OHdOIEqSz20g8o4dAYA8BG95LnFdpwSFP2h87ospwfaTyzzpjcxMFR0w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6k1fyt\"><span mpa-font-style=\"minydswh1xj4\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-size:20px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"minyq93c1va7\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minyq93tn99\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">资本市场的账本：</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6k1fyt\"><span mpa-font-style=\"minydswh1xj4\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-size:20px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"minyq93c1va7\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minyq93tn99\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">就看你 AI 怎么样</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6k1v0h\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"minydswhk8k\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">虽然苹果股价今年以来上涨了16%，但这在科技巨头中并不算亮眼，表现落后于许多同行。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6k15ap\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"minydswhbva\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">投资者担心的是投入与产出。微软和谷歌正在斥资数千亿美元建设 AI 数据中心、研发芯片和前沿模型。而苹果虽然声称正在“显著增加” AI 支出，但其策略截然不同：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6kr97\"><span mpa-font-style=\"minydswhvhd\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">·&nbsp;</span></span><b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">更少的基建投入</span></span></b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">苹果倾向于混合模式，不仅依赖自建的私有云计算，还通过与 OpenAI 合作，将 ChatGPT 整合进 Siri。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6ky0s\"><span mpa-font-style=\"minydswhtya\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">·&nbsp;</span></span><b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">端侧优先</span></span></b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">苹果坚持让 AI 在设备上运行，而非完全依赖云端，这虽然保护了隐私，但也限制了算力上限。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6ko7g\"><b mpa-font-style=\"minydswho1p\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">更让苹果头疼的是“后院起火”。</span></span></b></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6k1uj0\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"minydswhrfy\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">苹果传奇设计师乔纳森·艾维（Jony Ive）今年以64亿美元的价格将自己的初创公司 io 出售给了 OpenAI。艾维正与 OpenAI CEO 萨姆·奥特曼（Sam Altman）合作开发一款全新 AI 硬件。据悉，首批原型机已经完成，可能在不到两年内面世。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6k1a1p\"><span mpa-font-style=\"minydswh19c\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">分析师普遍认为，虽然自2007年 iPhone 推出以来，强大的用户忠诚度帮助苹果建立起坚不可摧的“护城河”，</span></span><b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">但下一代硬件革命很可能是由 AI 驱动。如果苹果不能在 AI 体验上尽快追平差距，其硬件霸主的地位将面临实质性威胁。</span></span></b></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6kss9\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"502851488\" data-ratio=\"0.15204678362573099\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"684\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e3903754&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FrwnawOsSCFp4iatBAbsJzvVraDq6Xh5OHbibjrtOUPcIJ97eDllknPibqJcjaTO0xclRf0UKBH8hLvEwbOEwtxiaAQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6k17oc\"><b mpa-font-style=\"minydswh4qo\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-size:20px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"minyr28w1vrk\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minyr29i2ce\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">业内反响：</span></span></b></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6k17oc\"><b mpa-font-style=\"minydswh4qo\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-size:20px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"minyr28w1vrk\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minyr29i2ce\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">苹果 AI 能翻盘么？</span></span></b></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6k20ou\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"minydswh1hxa\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">这次接任苹果 AI 主帅的苏布拉马尼亚或许能帮助苹果实现翻盘，毕竟他拥有超过20年的技术从业经验。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6kqe2\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"minydswhqci\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">苏布拉马尼亚专注于 AI 基础模型、NLP 和产品集成，曾贡献于谷歌和微软的标志性 AI 项目。职业生涯跨越研究与工程，强调“创新、可靠且高度个性化的 AI 体验”。苹果 CEO 库克也称赞其拥有“非凡的 AI 专长”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6k20n8\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"minydswh10zt\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">加入苹果后，苏布拉马尼亚将领导苹果的 AI 基础模型研究、机器学习开发和 AI 安全评估，推动 Siri 等产品的智能化升级。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6k1au6\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"minydswh20in\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">社交媒体X的用户也对这位新晋AI主帅寄予厚望。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6kl0r\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"minydswhmwz\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">前端工程师Jane Duru发文称，这次换帅释放出一个明确信号：苹果正在重构整个AI战略方向。但最值得玩味的是，苹果选择的接任者是有微软、谷歌双重背景的苏布拉马尼亚。这绝非随意之举。相当于苹果在默默承认：我们不能再承受一次AI时代的落后。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6kegv\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"minydswh148v\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">他认为，“这一转折点将定义未来十年的科技格局。因为若苹果此次转型失败，未来的操作系统之争将不再是iOS对阵安卓……而是拥有AI的公司对阵没有AI的公司。”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6k1lg7\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"minydswha78\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">开发人员Danny Franklin则认为，“随着苹果加倍投入AI创新，这一举措或将重塑开发者和企业将智能技术融入生态体系的方式，值得密切关注。”</span></span></p>\n  <figure style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6kvgz\">\n   <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"503047904\" data-ratio=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;background: none transparent;min-height: unset;object-fit: contain;width: 702.031px;height: auto;\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"750\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=db750b8f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FrwnawOsSCFrBt7hIgyyOl5rlDDp9ZN5quHVrNZtIkicic0uksCG8vtF2fnf2QYpYJeQdk2tOjbVIZIx0qTJ2puicQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  </figure>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6kjo3\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"minydswh12w5\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">或许资本市场的反应最为诚实。周一苹果股价上涨1.52%，收于每股283.10美元。</span></span></p>\n  <figure style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6kulq\">\n   <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"503047907\" data-ratio=\"0.8346666666666667\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;background: none transparent;min-height: unset;object-fit: contain;width: 702.031px;height: auto;\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"750\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5869f8dc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FrwnawOsSCFrBt7hIgyyOl5rlDDp9ZN5qWZxHZichL2OEOZ77On8LDGl4oPyG8picic3pqNrrVicmiaAMavE8IYsLlfQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  </figure>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6khy1\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"minydswh21yl\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">用户@graemethickins推测，“苹果任命微软谷歌前高管接棒退休AI负责人，这恐怕就是今天股价应声上涨的原因吧。”</span></span></p>\n  <figure style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6k1nvn\">\n   <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"503047908\" data-ratio=\"0.9653333333333334\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;background: none transparent;min-height: unset;object-fit: contain;width: 702.031px;height: auto;\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"750\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9bdf3aaa&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FrwnawOsSCFrBt7hIgyyOl5rlDDp9ZN5q9ib3ciciaLmZodz7LibXtp40XHG099unEtGeAdqickAzsHpy3aWPhxP22qg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  </figure>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minz61j9nac\"><img data-imgfileid=\"502851490\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.15204678362573099\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"684\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=030f7a1c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FrwnawOsSCFp4iatBAbsJzvVraDq6Xh5OHsDZQfsdibic3RFsRzTxlWDUxMnic9P9w6bYJL5bAJCtK9gH5dd5r7n4RQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6krej\"><b mpa-font-style=\"minydswh1wfl\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-size:20px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"minyrupj1zex\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minyruq11s6m\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">结语：</span></span></b></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6krej\"><b mpa-font-style=\"minydswh1wfl\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-size:20px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"minyrupj1zex\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minyruq11s6m\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">一场不能输的追击战</span></span></b></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6kl0z\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"minydswh1ub1\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">苏布拉马尼亚的上任，是苹果试图扭转局势的关键一步。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6kavc\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"minydswh1mes\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">他面临的任务清单极其艰巨：理顺混乱的 AI 开发流程、确保基础模型的安全与性能、并在2026年之前交付一个真正“聪明”的 Siri。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"minymy6k1bll\"><span mpa-font-style=\"minydg95c7p\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"minydswh1qca\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">苹果正在玩一场与微软、谷歌完全不同的游戏。它不追求最大的参数量，而追求最佳的软硬件整合体验。</span></span><b><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"color: #595959;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\" mpa-font-style=\"minydswhs3y\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">但在 AI 技术日新月异的今天，留给这位继任者翻盘的时间，确实不多了。</span></span></span></span></b></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "苹果任命前谷歌 DeepMind 高管 Amar Subramanya 为 AI 副总裁，以重振 Siri 并应对 AI 赛道落后局面，预示着苹果 AI 战略的重大调整。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "苹果任命前谷歌 DeepMind 高管 Amar Subramanya 为 AI 副总裁，以重振 Siri 并应对 AI 赛道落后局面，预示着苹果 AI 战略的重大调整。",
  "summary": "文章深入分析了苹果公司近期重大人事变动及其对 AI 战略的影响。因 Siri 表现不佳和被指在 AI 领域掉队，苹果宣布执掌 AI 七年的 John Giannandrea 卸任，并从竞争对手谷歌 DeepMind 和微软挖来实战派 Amar Subramanya 接任 AI 副总裁。此次换帅不仅是高层变动，更伴随着 AI 汇报线的调整，预示着苹果将 AI 深度整合进软件产品线，以期在明年为用户带来更个性化的 Siri 体验，并可能对 AI 团队进行大规模重组。文章探讨了苹果面临的“焦虑时刻”，包括 AI 战略不明确、核心功能跳票、以及与 OpenAI 等巨头的差距。最后，文章对新任高管能否帮助苹果在 AI 驱动的下一代硬件革命中翻盘进行了展望，强调这是一场苹果不能输的追击战。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "苹果任命 Amar Subramanya 为 AI 副总裁，旨在扭转 Siri 困境并加速 AI 发展",
      "explanation": "此举是苹果对外界质疑其 AI 落后的回应，通过引入拥有谷歌 DeepMind 和微软背景的实战派，期望在 AI 核心技术和产品集成上取得突破。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 汇报线调整预示苹果将 AI 深度整合进软件产品线，而非独立部门",
      "explanation": "新任副总裁向软件工程主管汇报，表明苹果正将 AI 视为核心软件能力进行强化，而非孤立发展，以实现更个性化的用户体验。"
    },
    {
      "point": "苹果在 AI 领域面临巨大挑战，包括战略不明确、核心功能跳票及市场竞争加剧",
      "explanation": "文章指出苹果在 AI 方面反应迟缓，产品缺乏惊艳感，且升级版 Siri 跳票，这对其在 AI 驱动的下一代硬件革命中的地位构成威胁。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "Siri 频频\"听不懂人话\"的掉线表现，不仅磨光了果粉的情怀，也终于逼得库克彻底\"破防\"了。",
    "这一架构调整释放了一个明确信号：苹果正在将 AI 从一个独立的战略部门，深度整合进软件产品线。",
    "问题根源在于，苹果似乎并不知道自己的 AI 战略到底是什么。",
    "若苹果此次转型失败，未来的操作系统之争将不再是 iOS 对阵安卓......而是拥有 AI 的公司对阵没有 AI 的公司。",
    "但在 AI 技术日新月异的今天，留给这位继任者翻盘的时间，确实不多了。"
